{"tid":1666192,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Dior繼續道歉！上海秀放《我和我的祖國》全場部落客看呆　網嘲：求生慾爆棚","createTime":"2019-10-21T01:23:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-27T05:59:31.000Z","uid":68738,"like":23,"dislike":223,"uniUserReply":83,"replies":[{"pid":"c53894452e143e18a3f887e7ee7e877dce688f66","tid":1666192,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T01:23:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2-ettoday-net.cdn.ampproject.org/ii/w1200/s/cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4452/d4452935.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2-ettoday-net.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fii%2Fw1200%2Fs%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4452%2Fd4452935.jpg&h=659bc780&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲迪奧上海發表會。（圖／翻攝自微博／DIOR迪奥）<br />\n<br />\n記者董美琪／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n國際品牌Dior 16日因員工在大學演講時，投影一張沒有台灣的中國地圖，引起大陸網友轟爆，Dior事後除了發出一份道歉聲明，表示尊重一個中國原則，19日更在Dior 2020春夏成衣系列上海發表秀上，現場播放大陸愛國歌曲《我和我的祖國》，影片也因此在網上瘋傳，引起大陸網友笑說「隔著屏幕都能感受到滿滿的求生慾&hellip;&hellip;」。<br />\n<br />\nDior 16日來到大陸某校園舉辦宣傳演講活動，但當他們投放大陸門市地圖在螢幕上時，現場卻有學生赫然驚呼「地圖怎麼少了台灣」，當場引起一陣譁然及鼓掌，雖然負責人解釋因為台灣面積太小，仍引起爭議，現場影片迅速在網上熱傳。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2-ettoday-net.cdn.ampproject.org/ii/w1200/s/cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4444/4444023.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2-ettoday-net.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fii%2Fw1200%2Fs%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4444%2F4444023.jpg&h=b57e68da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲因地圖風波，Dior日前急發聲明。（圖／翻攝自微博）<br />\n<br />\n迪奧17日凌晨2點，通過官微緊急發聲明，強調個別員工的錯誤言論不代表母公司LVMH和品牌的立場，公司已著手調查，並承諾予以嚴肅處理，「迪奧對中國的誠摯熱愛之心無可置疑。」<br />\n<br />\nDior似乎滅火成功，2020春夏成衣系列發布會19日在上海照常舉行，且閉幕後的派對還播放了大陸愛國歌曲《我和我的祖國》。<br />\n<br />\n從網友上傳的影片可發現，當派對上播放《我和我的祖國》時，現場人士立刻放下酒杯、停止跳舞，並舉起手機拍下這特別的一幕。<br />\n<br />\n影片被傳開後，多位大陸時尚部落客表示驚訝又好笑，網友聽了笑說，Dior播放這首歌曲充滿「隔著屏幕都能感受到滿滿的求生慾&hellip;&hellip;」、「識時務者為俊傑」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/amp/amp_news.php%3fnews_id=1561387\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Famp%2Famp_news.php%253fnews_id%3D1561387&d=IZFSAkWTwbXSesVVmoeERSukga04qSQtFIF%2FU0RrEoA%3D&h=6479c529\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/amp/amp_news.php%3fnews_id=1561387</a>"},{"pid":"8022bbfef19de3f9e007ca064503d69a4c3b07df","tid":1666192,"uid":57940,"like":201,"dislike":2,"score":199,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T01:38:04.000Z","msg":"即刻dum曬 d Dior 佢屌"},{"pid":"083ba81af7fa81e80e5ee243ce92b142b1c3ab7b","tid":1666192,"uid":18210,"like":235,"dislike":0,"score":235,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T01:44:55.000Z","msg":"根本呢個世界唔需要有呢d 名牌都可以生存到。 而全世界係大陸d on9 先覺得買係身份像徵同會肯比錢買。 呢d 所謂大集團就等支爆收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d48f84054dc913bce98f50a248b5543df02903c","tid":1666192,"uid":270956,"like":31,"dislike":2,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T01:45:14.000Z","msg":"好 cheap <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4cb95de926f838c29f9daa34420aebd568c137b","tid":1666192,"uid":148980,"like":63,"dislike":1,"score":62,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T01:46:49.000Z","msg":"奶共雖可恥但有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"030481f16fa3b757b2c4f2b3ef49c4ef16936876","tid":1666192,"uid":127929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T01:47:03.000Z","msg":"舔中舐共<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9599ab693396ec47dde0da9b974fab6291f513af","tid":1666192,"uid":68738,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"d4cb95de926f838c29f9daa34420aebd568c137b","tid":1666192,"uid":148980,"like":63,"dislike":1,"score":62,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T01:46:49.000Z","msg":"奶共雖可恥但有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T01:47:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b47f1cee01259c0fd886c57196389d0d1007cef4",